{"about_the_game":"The tomb of the very first Magi has been discovered, and with it, whispers of riches and treasures untold. That is, if you can get your hands on the mystical sigils that line the tomb\u2019s walls\u2026<br><br>Pick your party and embark on an unforgettable journey to obtain the Sigil of the Magi!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Skill-based cardslinging combat, with the card rack feature to mitigate RNG<br></li><li> Multiple factions, classes, and card choices make for countless of ways to win<br></li><li> Go on a roguelite adventure by making impactful choices that affect your journey through each of the three game worlds</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/new_steam_2.gif?t=1706586860\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/heroes_1.gif?t=1706586860\" /><br><br>Every champion has a unique card deck of active and passive skills. Choose a pre-made faction or mix and match to suit your playstyle. Craft a finely-honed deck and prove yourself worthy to finally wield the Sigil of the Magi!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/FEATURES.png?t=1706586860\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Countless decks and ways to win</h2>With unique class-based cards, passive abilities, and multiple unlockable classes, there are plenty of strategic options you can experiment with on every run. Drafting a synergistic deck is key to overcoming challenging encounters.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/new_steam_1.gif?t=1706586860\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Obtain powerful, game-changing relics</h2>The Sigil may be the end goal, but Relics provide all kinds of effects and benefits along your journey, and are not tied to any champion. Relics can affect the entire party and sometimes have prerequisites that must be met before they become effective. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/relics.png?t=1706586860\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Conquer your fate with the card rack</h2>Don\u2019t let RNG ruin your run \u2014 store your cards on the card rack, reserving them for use on a future turn. Mitigate bad hands by planning ahead.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/new_card_rack.gif?t=1706586860\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Choose your own path towards the Sigil</h2>Make your way through 3 dynamic worlds full of fateful choices hidden secrets and face challenging bosses at the end of each journey. Choose your path wisely and your party will thrive, not just survive.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781960/extras/map3.png?t=1706586860\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Iron Claw","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1781960/e541d757ab4e62c59315615a99269f0aa6030d1c.jpg"},{"name":"Bandit Chief","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1781960/078841f8b1b3223fa881b6f55650e4e838a4c410.jpg"},{"name":"Hunter Supreme","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1781960/9f04723be1229939671a662fdd67d20f91e22f6d.jpg"},{"name":"The Apostles","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1781960/a307618db97fff8c2c507d271f21f439236f8fd7.jpg"},{"name":"The Demi Divine","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1781960/a7c75833a8fe64e2e08ac0641a7baad59a7de33a.jpg"},{"name":"Chief Rector","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1781960/0377bcacc6cc0d69d13ff872b48b06ffc0182ade.jpg"},{"name":"The Oversee